# Keep the website public and the private data out of the repository.
# IMPORTANT: never commit a real, filled-in invitation list with people's
# names, emails, or phone numbers. The templates in data/ are fictional and
# safe to commit. If you create a real private copy, name it like the line
# below so Git ignores it.
data/invitation-list-private.csv
data/*-private.csv
data/*-private.txt

# Private guest list spreadsheets (contain real names and phone numbers).
# These must never be published to the public website.
docs/Book.xlsx
*.xlsx

# Local notes
notes.local.md
